[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0210","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0210.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0089","title":"IBM AIX libDtSvc 库本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 libDtSvc 库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向受影响服务发送超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可获取 root 权限，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，无法远程利用，危害等级为高危。CVSS v2 评分 7.2，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0089"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-10-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 AIX 4.3.2 及以上维护级别，或安装 IBM APAR IX45523 补丁以修复 libDtSvc 库缓冲区溢出漏洞。临时缓解措施可限制不可信用户对 CDE 组件的本地访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0089","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0089"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0210.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0181","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0072","title":"IBM AIX xdat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 xdat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 xdat 程序发送特制的超长输入参数，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用，成功利用后可完全控制受影响的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0072"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.907","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 为该漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（对应 AIX 4.x 及更早版本的 xdat 缓冲区溢出修复），或升级到包含该修复的 AIX 维护级别。临时缓解措施：执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/xdat` 移除 xdat 的 setuid root 权限，阻止非授权用户以 root 权限执行该程序；如业务不需要 DMI（Desktop Management Interface）子系统，可卸载相应文件集或禁用 xdat 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0072"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0169","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0169.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0068","title":"PHP PHP/FI mylog 脚本任意文件读取漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 的 mylog CGI 脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制的 URL 参数，读取目标服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 1.0、FI 2.0 及 FI 2.0 b10 版本，利用方式简单，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0068"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.230","remediation":"立即移除服务器上 PHP/FI 1.0/2.0 的 mylog/mlog CGI 脚本文件，或升级至 PHP 3.0 及以上版本，该漏洞在后继版本中已修复。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中禁止对该脚本的外部访问，并将 PHP/FI 替换为受支持的 PHP 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3396","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19553","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0068","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0068.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j2h3-fmf6-5vc4/GHSA-j2h3-fmf6-5vc4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/php_arbitrary_file_access.nasl","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/PHP_FI%201.0_2.0%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-0068).html","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0068.yaml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0169.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0169.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0169.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0375","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0375.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0192","title":"RedHat Linux telnetd TERMCAP 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Telnet 守护进程中的 tgetent() 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 TERMCAP 环境变量，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 RedHat Linux 6.0 及 Slackware Linux 4.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0192"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:51.540","remediation":"立即禁用 telnet 服务：编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释 telnet 行后重启 inetd（或执行 service telnet stop），升级到不再提供 telnetd 的现代发行版；迁移至 SSH（OpenSSH）替代远程管理。如必须保留 telnet，可安装 TCP Wrapper 配置 hosts.allow/hosts.deny 限制源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0192","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19465","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0192.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/x0rz/EQGRP/blob/0c2354ff1073099b2aa417030b3167ec29d7279c/README.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0192","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0192.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0192.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0375.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0567","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0346","title":"PHP PHP/FI mlog 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0346 是 PHP 的 mlog CGI 脚本中存在的一个任意文件读取漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标服务器上该脚本发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用参数注入的方式读取服务器上的任意敏感文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），导致信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 PHP 版本，攻击条件低（无需认证、远程利用）。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0346"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.993","remediation":"升级至 PHP 3.0.17 或更高版本（已修复该 CGI 漏洞），或删除/禁用服务器上的 mlog CGI 脚本。若无法升级，请在 Web 服务器配置中禁止执行 /cgi-bin/php/fi/mlog 等路径，并设置文件系统权限限制 CGI 进程仅访问必要目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3397","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0346","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0346.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph/GHSA-9fhg-rgm9-gqph.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-misc.rules","https://github.com/mtesauro/owasp-wte/blob/e4c016caf67d59634f309f2a1feeed7dc9515abe/temp-projects/spikeproxy/contents/opt/owasp/spikeproxy/scan_database.db","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/php_arbitrary_file_access.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0346.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0567.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0160","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0160.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0061","title":"BSD Line Printer Daemon (lpd) 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"BSD 行式打印机守护进程（lpd）存在远程代码执行漏洞，源于其对打印任务处理过程中缺乏充分的访问控制与输入验证。远程攻击者无需认证即可向运行 lpd 服务的目标系统发送特制的打印请求，实现任意文件创建、删除或远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Linux 及 BSD 系列操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0061"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.180","remediation":"禁用 lpd 服务（`killall lpd` 并移除启动项），升级到已修复版本，或使用 TCP Wrapper 限制端口 515 仅允许受信主机访问；对于不需要网络打印的系统，建议直接卸载 lpd 替代为 CUPS 或 LPRng 等现代打印系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0061"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0160.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0213","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0090","title":"IBM AIX rcp 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 系统 rcp 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 rcp 命令提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。利用需要本地用户身份，成功利用后攻击者可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0090"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.733","remediation":"IBM 已在 AIX 4.x 版本的 APAR IY09308 中修复此漏洞，建议更新 bos.rte.net_filesystem fileset 至包含该 APAR 的维护级别。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/bin/rcp 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/rcp，或禁用 r-commands 服务（rshd、rexecd）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0090"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0458","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0272","title":"Slmail POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Slmail 3.0.2421 及 2.5 版本的 POP3 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标主机的 POP3 端口（默认 110）发送特制恶意数据包，导致服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成正常的邮件收发功能中断。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需复杂权限即可触发，影响运行 Slmail 服务的邮件服务器系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0272"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.843","remediation":"Slmail 产品已停止维护多年，建议迁移至现代受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix、Exchange 等）。如仍需继续使用，可在防火墙层面限制 POP3 端口（110）仅允许受信任 IP 段访问，并监控异常连接流量作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0488","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0294","title":"Microsoft Windows WINS 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 WINS 服务存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议向目标 WINS 服务器发送特制请求，删除 WINS 数据库中的所有记录，导致网络名称解析服务失效。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需认证即可利用 SNMP 管理接口实施拒绝服务攻击，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0294"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.503","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 或更高版本补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙及主机层面限制 SNMP 服务 (UDP 161) 的访问来源，仅允许受信任的管理主机访问，并在 WINS 服务器上配置 SNMP 读写团体字串为复杂值，避免使用默认的 \"public\"。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0294","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20564","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0294","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0294.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g6mp-qfqw-f6cf/GHSA-g6mp-qfqw-f6cf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/wins_cve.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0497","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0300","title":"Sun Solaris NIS+ nis_cachemgr 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 缓存管理器存在安全设计缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞向缓存中注入恶意的 NIS+ 服务器信息。当客户端查询网络信息服务时，将连接到攻击者控制的伪造服务器，导致敏感信息（如用户凭据、主机配置）被窃取或服务遭到劫持。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0300"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.247","remediation":"针对 Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 漏洞，建议立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #155 中提供的官方补丁。如运行 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 且无法打补丁，应在网络边界通过防火墙限制对 nis_cachemgr 端口（TCP/UDP 387）的访问，仅允许受信 NIS+ 服务器通信。由于 NIS+ 已停止维护，建议迁移至基于 LDAP 的命名服务以获得长期安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/155","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0300","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0300.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--12792e2d-cd40-4418-b42c-679d4e4e14e3.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0541","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0326","title":"HP HP-UX mediainit 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 mediainit 媒体设备初始化程序存在安全漏洞。该程序用于初始化磁带机等存储设备，但由于对输入参数缺乏充分验证，本地攻击者可利用该缺陷，通过向 mediainit 程序传递特制参数触发漏洞，导致系统机密信息部分泄露、系统数据被部分篡改或服务部分不可用。此漏洞为本地利用，无需额外认证，攻击复杂度低，影响 HP-UX 系统多个版本，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。HP 已通过安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0326"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.543","remediation":"立即应用 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9710-071 提供的官方补丁。如无法打补丁，可移除 mediainit 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/mediainit），并限制可执行权限仅授予信任的管理员用户组。建议将 HP-UX 系统升级至包含该修复的后续版本（如 11.0 以上），因 10.x 系列已终止技术支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9710-071"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0541.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0329","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0329.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0160","title":"Cisco IOS PPP CHAP 认证绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 设备的 PPP CHAP 认证机制存在安全绕过漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用该漏洞建立未授权的 PPP 连接，从而获得目标网络的访问权限，可能导致敏感信息泄露、数据篡改或服务中断。该漏洞影响多款经典 Cisco IOS 设备，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互，CVSS v2 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0160"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.1 或更高版本（该漏洞已在 11.1 及后续维护版本中修复）。如无法立即升级，可在 PPP 接口配置 `access-class` ACL 限制仅允许可信源 IP 建立拨号连接，并在全局配置下使用 `no service tcp-small-servers` 和 `no service udp-small-servers` 关闭不必要的小型服务以减小攻击面。对于仍在运行不受支持老版本 IOS 的设备，建议迁移至当前受支持的 IOS 版本或替换为现代网络设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0329.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0368","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0368.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0185","title":"Sun SunOS/Solaris FTP 服务数据端口信任滥用远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统中 FTP 服务与 rlogin 服务之间存在信任关系绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可利用 FTP 协议的数据端口（20/tcp）主动连接至目标主机上受信任的 rlogin 服务，绕过正常认证机制实现远程命令执行。该漏洞源于 FTP 服务器被目标主机配置为信任主机，攻击者无需任何凭证即可通过构造特殊 FTP 会话获得对目标系统的完全控制，影响 SunOS 5.3~5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.3~2.5.1 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0185"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #156 提供的对应 Solaris 版本补丁。停止使用 rlogin/rsh 服务，改用 SSH 进行远程管理；删除 /etc/hosts.equiv 及所有用户的 .rhosts 文件以消除主机间隐式信任关系；配置 FTP 服务禁止 PORT 命令反弹连接至非 FTP 端口（如在 wu-ftpd 中设置 refuse-connection 规则），阻断反弹攻击路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0368.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0490","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0490.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0295","title":"Sun Solaris sysdef 命令本地内核内存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中的 sysdef 命令存在内核内存信息泄露漏洞。本地普通用户可通过执行 sysdef 命令读取内核内存中的敏感数据，进而获取内核地址布局等关键信息，结合其他漏洞可导致权限提升至 root 级别。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.4/2.5/2.5.1 及 SunOS 5.3-5.5.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。Sun 已发布安全公告 157 提供修复方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0295"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01","updated":"1997-10-01","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin 157 提供的官方补丁。鉴于 SunOS 5.3~5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.4~2.5.1 均已停止维护，建议升级到受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11.4 或更高版本。如无法升级，临时缓解措施为：以 root 权限执行 chmod 700 /usr/sbin/sysdef 限制 sysdef 命令的访问权限，仅允许 root 用户执行，同时移除 sysdef 的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/sysdef），防止本地普通用户通过该命令读取内核内存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0490.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0363","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0182","title":"Samba Samba 1.9.19 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 1.9.19 及更早版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 Samba 服务发送特制的超长密码字符串触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 Samba 1.9.19 的 Unix/Linux 系统，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0182"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.523","remediation":"立即升级 Samba 至 2.0.0 及以上版本（1.9.19 系列已停止维护，2.0.0 修复了该缓冲区溢出问题）。如无法立即升级，可在 smb.conf 中设置 hosts allow/deny 限制可访问 SMB 服务的源 IP 范围，并在防火墙层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 139 和 445 的外部访问以临时缓解风险。现代 Linux 发行版应直接使用系统包管理器更新至当前受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-110.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20308","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0182.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0182","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/292.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/jbeasl7/openvas-feed-sync-local/blob/02ed2a2b96fc19fd49a4be810f3493abb776ec4e/openvas-feeds/nvt-feed/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml"}]